Author: mud_octopus
Text: Saaaaaaaaame.   I actually told someone who had made 2 comments, cause I was scared they'd make more and I really hate it (like love/hate but just do not want). Just told them I have an ED and the comments are harmful.   I'm a full adult, and pretty secure in other ways. I don't want my ED to be common knowledge, and mostly find it embarrassing, but I also want people to STOP COMMENTING ON PEOPLES BODIES UNLESS INVITED TO DO SO.   Wow, I got heated at the end there, but really.
